.SH "OPTIONS"
.sp
\fB\-\-bins\fP
.RS 4
Adds \fI/bin\fP, \fI/sbin\fP, \fI/share/man\fP and \fI/share/info\fP
to parent dirname of \fBFILE|DIR\fP argument.
If no \fBFILE|DIR\fP argument is provided, then \fIgit top\fP is used (added with and without \fItests/\fP).
The output (\fI\-\-export\fP option implied) will have \fI$PATH\fP, \fI$MANPATH\fP and \fI$INFOPATH\fP updated to be used with \fIeval\fP.
